<ElliciumText Anchor="progressbar#progressbar-min-max-values" TextStyle="TextStyle.H5" TagName="TagName.H2" class="rz-pt-12 rz-mb-6">
    ProgressBar Min and Max values
</ElliciumText>
<ElliciumText TextStyle="TextStyle.Body1" class="rz-mb-8">
    By default, the value range is between 0 and 100.
    Use the <code>Min</code> and <code>Max</code> properties to set a custom range.
</ElliciumText>
